3a8965510e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/92bb9dcf6209393c47bb033a8965510e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lh23\" class=\"reviewer-name\">lh23</a> <span class=\"review-date\">Август 28, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Have been testing Optimole with a new sites and am impressed so far.  Support has also been very good with fast response times.  Would be nice to have custom image subdomains in a cheaper plan.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Faster Loading Time</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/muaazbinsarfaraz\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b30d6aaf28e6d1b43c5f5ee1d0fffe17?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b30d6aaf28e6d1b43c5f5ee1d0fffe17?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/muaazbinsarfaraz\" class=\"reviewer-name\">muaazbinsarfaraz</a> <span class=\"review-date\">Август 25, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I am excited to see how at no cost I could get my site to respond better by utilizing CDN. I am currently using the freemium, but plan to move towards the premium as store grows.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Awesome tool</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/digiveljet\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f2f58bc574aa8de96e04ff69dcf131e7?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f2f58bc574aa8de96e04ff69dcf131e7?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/digiveljet\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Jesse Kivivuori <small>(digiveljet)</small></a> <span class=\"review-date\">Август 23, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Really awesome and valuable tool! Works like as it should be.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">GREAT PLUGIN - OUTSTANDING SUPPORT</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nitro12345\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9e0511e1410b40fdfa88560989f06f5b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9e0511e1410b40fdfa88560989f06f5b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nitro12345\" class=\"reviewer-name\">nitro12345</a> <span class=\"review-date\">Август 19, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Using Divi Builder I had some issues of the CDN links replacing my images, that caused a lot of 301 redirects.\nIt was not an issue of the plugin but of Divi Theme.\nThanks to their outstanding support it runs 100% smoothly now.\nAmazing!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Gracias, me ayuda mcuho</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/angelrojo209\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1da67630d3621d2771ef79509bb43c1b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1da67630d3621d2771ef79509bb43c1b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/angelrojo209\" class=\"reviewer-name\">angelrojo209</a> <span class=\"review-date\">Август 8, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">es un excelente trabajo, gracias por compartir</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:101:\"Improve your site loading speed by delivering optimized WebP image for each device. Lazy load&hellip;\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:54:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:4:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/optimole-wp/assets/screenshot-1.jpeg?rev=1991524\";s:7:\"caption\";s:14:\"Welcome screen\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/optimole-wp/assets/screenshot-2.jpeg?rev=1991521\";s:7:\"caption\";s:14:\"Connect screen\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/optimole-wp/assets/screenshot-3.jpeg?rev=1991521\";s:7:\"caption\";s:16:\"Plugin dashboard\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/optimole-wp/assets/screenshot-4.jpeg?rev=1991523\";s:7:\"caption\";s:15:\"Plugin settings\";}}s:8:\"versions\";a:18:{s:5:\"1.0.1\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.1.0.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.2\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.1.0.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.3\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.1.0.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.4\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.1.0.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.5\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.1.0.5.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.0\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.1.1.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.1\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.1.1.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.2\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.1.1.2.zip\";s:5:\"2.0.0\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.2.0.0.zip\";s:5:\"2.0.1\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpres