lass=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Muy practico</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nilsonluna\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3259545ab8c6ab5bd15c030c2de0f827?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3259545ab8c6ab5bd15c030c2de0f827?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nilsonluna\" class=\"reviewer-name\">nilsonluna</a> <span class=\"review-date\">Сентябрь 15, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">muy practico, muy bueno, fácil de usar </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">One of the best plugins</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/chaudhry111\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9716e4b623e64341076a55984e6e33c6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9716e4b623e64341076a55984e6e33c6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/chaudhry111\" class=\"reviewer-name\">chaudhry111</a> <span class=\"review-date\">Сентябрь 15, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Most advanced features and easy to use. Thank you</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Better than Divi...BIG TIME! Support not so great.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/norfolkpete\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c10286a4dacd19e24d96ac0110763419?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c10286a4dacd19e24d96ac0110763419?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/norfolkpete\" class=\"reviewer-name\">NorfolkUK <small>(NorfolkPete)</small></a> <span class=\"review-date\">Сентябрь 15, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">We\'ve used Divi for years however we decide to give Elementor a spin on a dev site as we needed to upgrade and redesign a handful of our websites.\n\nWe quickly decided Elementor was far superior and much lighter than Divi, super flexible and with a ton of features you simply don\'t get with Divi.\n\nWe\'re now rebuilding all our own branded sites using Elementor Pro.\n\nReason for 4 Stars...support isn\'t the best. There are a couple of Facebook communities just for Elementor and they are invaluable in offering prompt help and advice. Elementor, you seriously need to up your game with support.\n\nOther than that, excellent builder.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Magnífico</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pacoalarcon\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/13f7b0da6ece56a65f21a5b961bc7c9e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/13f7b0da6ece56a65f21a5b961bc7c9e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pacoalarcon\" class=\"reviewer-name\">pacoalarcon</a> <span class=\"review-date\">Сентябрь 15, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Un trabajo fantástico.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\