><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/weglot/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=2009075\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/weglot/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=2009075\" alt=\"Пример на стороне пользователя: кнопка переключения языка на странице\"></a><p>Пример на стороне пользователя: кнопка переключения языка на странице</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/weglot/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=2009083\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/weglot/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=2009083\" alt=\"Страница настроек Weglot Translate\"></a><p>Страница настроек Weglot Translate</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/weglot/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=2009083\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/weglot/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=2009083\" alt=\"Консоль Weglot Translate, редактирование перевода\"></a><p>Консоль Weglot Translate, редактирование перевода</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/weglot/assets/screenshot-4.jpg?rev=2009083\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/weglot/assets/screenshot-4.jpg?rev=2009083\" alt=\"Weglot Translate visual editor\"></a><p>Weglot Translate visual editor</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:15254:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">I think the best plugin for this use!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ricky093\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/294ffb0477801d5d6298197bcd5fa36f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/294ffb0477801d5d6298197bcd5fa36f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ricky093\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ricky093</a> <span class=\"review-date\">Сентябрь 12, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I honestly have no words to describe above all the customer service of this fantastic plugin. I was looking for a plugin to translate my ecommerce in multilingual and after several searches, I came across them. I think it is one of the few plugins around to be so complete as it gives you the ability to automatically translate the site (my case since I have more than 2k products) but also manually fix the translations you want. The real challenge was to fix the data and banner processing policies. The support was very kind to help me (otherwise I would never have succeeded) and they took care of solving the problem. Given the cost, given the possibilities that Weglot offers, I can only recommend it to all those who want to make their site multilingual. A support so available, I rarely saw it so Thanks a lot guys, you were fantastic !!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Amazing Translation plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kafaltech\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/51003b6fcc8b7ed42901620895e86114?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/51003b6fcc8b7ed42901620895e86114?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kafaltech\" class=\"reviewer-name\">kafaltech</a> <span class=\"review-date\">Сентябрь 12, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This is simply the best translation app to use if you need multilingual websites. It literally saved me hours and hours of translation work and i was able to translate enterprise level websites in a day almost (including pdf files and images). Another great feature, The auto translator, even tho, you have sometimes to manually re correct some words (for french per instance), it saves you tones of hours of manual translation and all you have to do is just edit and adjust the translated version that the auto translator did for you directly via the admin section. Easy and Quick.\n\nThank you Weglot. Please keep up the good work. Its a life saver tool for developers who works with multilingual websites.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fast and Easy</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ggeeky\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d6bb69e0c22f8f9ce3322c19fe0ff012?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d6bb69e0c22f8f9ce3322c19fe0ff012?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ggeeky\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ggeeky</a> <span class=\"review-date\">Сентябрь 3, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The plugin itself is very easy to setup. Their translation management is also very user friendly. Top-notch support (even for harder situations).\n\nI would definitely recommend WeGlot over other plugins because it does not impact on your database and rarely encurs conflicts with other plugins.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">The best!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/monseviana\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/69864df8e3a73f39d4c9d88442936e05?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/69864df8e3a73f39d4c9d88442936e05?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/monseviana\" class=\"reviewer-name\">monseviana</a> <span class=\"review-date\">Август 30, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">friendly platform.\nExcellent support!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Easy to use, just a few minutes work!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rogierlansink\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5f8cf13daa22a9e9534e0477354367ca?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5f8cf13daa22a9e9534e0477354367ca?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rogierlansink\" class=\"reviewer-name\">rogierlansink</a> <span class=\"review-date\">Август 28, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Very good!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Support when moving translation inbetween domains</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/wbergler\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6bfe8dbe6d87aa2d98d5311bcd2d1aa4?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6bfe8dbe6d87aa2d98d5311bcd2d1aa4?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/wbergler\" class=\"reviewer-name\">wbergler</a> <span class=\"review-date\">Август 27, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Got very fast support from Christoph when having some trouble to moe a complete website from one domain o another. Very responsive and with hi quality! much appreciated</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simple plugin for online translation</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/stuarteasiserv\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d8a3686fe0b2f85b1a459b7a12681a07?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d8a3686fe0b2f85b1a459b7a12681a07?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/stuarteasiserv\" class=\"reviewer-name\">stuarteasiserv</a> <span class=\"review-date\">Август 21, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Really easy to install and get working. Support team are very helpful too and respond quickly to any request. Works best on smaller sites and is a great out of the box solution.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">The Perfect Solution!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/leighketchum\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e27f387f4b42830bd75afeecd79cade4?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e27f387f4b42830bd75afeecd79cade4?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/leighketchum\" class=\"reviewer-name\">leighketchum</a> <span class=\"review-date\">Август 19, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Well-crafted and the ONLY translation plugin that REALLY does translate. It works so well and has saved us countless hours of work. Plus great (fast and smart) support! Thank you WEGLOT for this exceptional plugin!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">EXTRAORDINARIO!!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anadeltoro\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7942dee293b0dd4a46873a096ac3a7fe?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7942dee293b0dd4a46873a096ac3a7fe?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anadeltoro\" class=\"reviewer-name\">anadeltoro</a> <span class=\"review-date\">Август 16, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Probé alrededor de 5 plugins de traducción y el mejor es Weglot, lo recomiendo ampliamente, además que el soporte es excelente, resuelven todas las dudas incluso ofrecen entrar al sitio para ayudar directamente.\n\nGracias Weglot!\n\nAna del Toro</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Perfect plugin and awesome support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons d