idth=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bhenselmann\" class=\"reviewer-name\">bhenselmann</a> <span class=\"review-date\">Август 14, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I changed from RJ Quickcharts to the Visualizer plugin, because RJ Quickcharts was not longer maintained. There are some advantages and some disadvantages of both, but the main advantage of Visualizer is, that it is available for actual WordPress and PHP versions.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Отличный плагин.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/memnokh\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cd86ac19bc3d3c89fbc304f49aca63e6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cd86ac19bc3d3c89fbc304f49aca63e6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/memnokh\" class=\"reviewer-name\">memnokh</a> <span class=\"review-date\">Июнь 24, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Легок в обращении и настройке в нужный вид.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Does what it says</h4>\n